  "lines": [
    {
      "lineNumber": 1,
      "text": "Office Memorandum • UNITED STATES GOVERNMENT",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 2,
      "text": "TO : Director, FBI DATE: July 31, 1952",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 3,
      "text": "FROM : SAC, Indianapolis (62-0)",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 4,
      "text": "SUBJECT: FLYING SAUCERS SEEN NEAR THESSALON LAKE,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 5,
      "text": "ONTARIO, CANADA, JULY 27, 1952",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 6,
      "text": "MISCELLANEOUS - INFORMATION CONCERNING",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "text": "Dr. [REDACTED] Kokomo,",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "text": "Indiana, on July 30, 1952 advised Special Agent [REDACTED]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "text": "that on July 27, 1952 at approximately 10:00 A.M.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "text": "while fishing in the back waters of Thessalon Lake,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "Ontario, Canada, he noticed a formation of bombing planes,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "sixteen to twenty in number, in two groups flying south",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "at a height estimated by him to be four or five miles.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "Dr. [REDACTED] stated that the planes went over the",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "lake, suddenly dropped objects at first thought by him",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "to be parachutes. He continued that these objects fell",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "straight down for a short time, then suddenly spurted vapor",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "and at a high rate of speed flew off in a southwesterly",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "direction.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "Dr. [REDACTED] was unable to identify the nationality",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "of the planes, but stated that they had twin trails of",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "bluish smoke. He further stated that the objects which",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "had been dropped from the planes had a single trail of",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "bluish smoke.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "He stated that he had been accompanied on his fishing",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "trip by [REDACTED], Kokomo, Indiana. Dr. [REDACTED] had no",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "further information concerning instant planes or the objects",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "dropped by them.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "Dr. [REDACTED] was referred to the FBI by [REDACTED],",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "President of the First National Bank of Kokomo, Indiana,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "who advised that Dr. [REDACTED] enjoyed a good reputation in",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "Kokomo.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "UACB, no further action will be taken in this matter.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "The above is being forwarded for the information of the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "Bureau in the event they desire to communicate this infor-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "mation to the Air Force.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "162-73774-285",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "text": "HSK:bjk",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
